title: Jason Dill Skate Off
description:
Jason Dill stopped by etnies last week to play Greater Manchester UK contest winner, Joseph O’Shaughnessy, in a long distance head-to-head EA SKATE 2 battle. The comp ran on the SKATE 2 website and in skate shops across 10 European countries.
Joe was randomly picked the winner out of the more than 135,000 correct SKATE 2 trivia answers.
